{"tid":1028883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7旬病婦新田圍邨墮樓亡　分屍慘死","createTime":"2019-02-19T22:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T22:38:54.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f577704bd6b3b57b7b1565a86b7fd872ef62d15","tid":1028883,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T22:22:24.000Z","msg":"沙田一名病婦高處墮下不治。今日(20日)凌晨4時56分，一名老婦在新田圍邨欣圍樓11樓梯間墮樓分屍慘死，右手在簷篷上，上下身分開兩部分在欣圍樓對開地面，保安員發現報案。救護員到場證實已經不治。警員用帳篷遮蓋屍體，並登樓調查，發現婦人已經年過70，多年受病患困擾墜樓輕生，病婦墮樓原因無可疑。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=cc71f304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190220/mobile/bkn-20190220051323284-0220_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190220%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190220051323284-0220_00822_001.html&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=5d28cf7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190220/mobile/bkn-20190220051323284-0220_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"06a632f98449ace264313c67a239c1b68102b000","tid":1028883,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T22:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9603d2ffcc52154cf1bbb1ca420d335259fb48","tid":1028883,"uid":220701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T22:32:28.000Z","msg":"到2019<br />\n安樂死都重未有<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.